{"tid":1189582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"既然搞到達哥休台，大家就應該喺69更努力出嚟抗爭","createTime":"2019-06-07T00:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T02:33:07.000Z","uid":25367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1d58c5b82b544665c01630a0571a77f657f9bb","tid":1189582,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:33:10.000Z","msg":"達哥可能有佢難處唔可以開聲，亦可能係佢立場真係變咗。但無論如何，喺民情凶湧嘅時間，達哥好不幸成為磨芯。社會運動就係some will fall and some will live，而達哥不幸做咗fall嗰嗰<br />\n相信大家咁大反應都只因為一直以嚟都支持達哥，其實大家都唔希望達哥從此摺埋。睇咗咁多年達哥，我希望佢可以重新振作<br />\n<br />\n雖然好遺憾但事到如今都冇辦法挽回，既然達哥因為大家聲討而休台退下火線，大家好應該負起責任69出嚟努力抗爭"},{"pid":"c4715828640056493c142f6b9217f93832f1ac93","tid":1189582,"uid":25367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RS9NWc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RS9NWc.gif&h=37263d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前人失敗嘅事，今次會由香港人做到"},{"pid":"52db06e1f9d9f4eece06ae4773f517544da4185c","tid":1189582,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018adf255c8bd2eb92b25dd43909352fe7263dc3","tid":1189582,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"依家重針著達哥既事好明顯想攪分化"},{"pid":"b41447111ea4765a12b19b46af3cf5a69d9253cb","tid":1189582,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}